type: software
title: "Multi-Agent Workflow for Biomedical Literature Review"
abstract: >
  A three-agent pipeline (Retriever, Summarizer, Verifier) that retrieves,
  summarizes, and fact-checks PubMed Central Open Access articles for a given
  biomedical research query. Built as an AI engineering portfolio case study.
